Eligibility Verification: Includes age, residency, KYC, fraud, and credit checks specific to the current account requirements.
Employment & Income: Collects employment status, monthly income, and tax residency details.
Fraud & Credit Checks: Performs real-time fraud and credit evaluations for secure onboarding.
Onboarding Steps:
Review personal details
Set card preferences (digital or physical)
Confirm account setup
Completion:
Issues a welcome pack (physical or digital)
Provides a debit card, ready for immediate use
This streamlined process ensures efficient and thorough account setup for eligible Solus Barclaycard customers.
